INSTALL:
========


Table of contents:
==================

    * Minimum Requirements
  
    * Installation

    * Run Test

Minimum Requirements
====================

 *Required Software Packages:

	* Perl 5.16 or above, installed with multithread support, and following Perl (CPAN) modules:
		Scalar::Util
                Data::Dumper
                Parallel::ForkManager
                Getopt::Long
                experimental
                SVG
                File::Spec
                List::Util
                Math::CDF
                Try::Tiny
                JSON

	* Python3	
	
	* Bowtie:An ultra-fast short read aligner, both version1.0 and version 2.0.
        
	* Samtools:provide various utilities for manipulating alignments in the SAM
          format, including sorting, merging, indexing and generating alignments in
          a per-position format(V1.9).
        
	* Tapir:Designed for the prediction of plant microRNA targets
        
	* Bedtools:A flexible suite of utilities for comparing genomic features
          Biochemistry of multidrug resistance mediated by the multidrug transporter.
        
	* ViennaRNA:For RNA Comparison and Secondary Structure Prediction (>=V2)
        
	* R and R Packages:
                seqinr
                XML
                RCurl
                data.table
                ggpubr
                jsonlite
                GOstats
                GenomicAlignments
                GenomicFeatures

 *Other program included in the distribution:

	* sRNAtools/program/external/megablast
	
	* sRNAtools/program/external/ShortStack
	
	* sRNAtools/program/mireap
	
	* sRNAtools/program/mirtrace

	* sRNAtools/program/phasiRNAClassifier

	* sRNAtools/program/PHASIS

	* sRNAtools/program/TargetFinder_1.6
	
Installation Packages
=====================
	* Perl (http://www.perl.org/)

	* Python3 (https://www.python.org/)

	* Bowtie (https://sourceforge.net/projects/bowtie-bio/files/bowtie2/2.3.4.3/bowtie2-2.3.4.3-linux-x86_64.zip)
		 (https://sourceforge.net/projects/bowtie-bio/files/bowtie/1.2.2/bowtie-1.2.2-linux-x86_64.zip)
    
	* Samtools (https://github.com/samtools/samtools/releases/download/1.9/samtools-1.9.tar.bz2)
        
        * Tapir (http://bioinformatics.psb.ugent.be/webtools/tapir/tapir-1.2.tar.gz)
        
        * Bedtools (https://github.com/arq5x/bedtools2/releases/download/v2.25.0/bedtools-2.25.0.tar.gz)
        
        * ViennaRNA (https://www.tbi.univie.ac.at/RNA/download/sourcecode/2_4_x/ViennaRNA-2.4.10.tar.gz)
        
        * R (https://www.r-project.org/)

	Note:Different computers may exist some differences, to access the official documentation.

Run Test
============
	Start an analysis test by the following command:
	
	perl run_fungi.pl -infile test_data/SRR1583952.fa -jobid SRR1583952

	






